cs.DB, cs.LO, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.SE. 

This paper deals with query answering and optimization for Datalog+ programs, which are commonly used in databases and knowledge representation. Therefore, cs.DB (Databases) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves logical reasoning and complexity analysis, which are relevant to cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The use of algorithms and data structures for query answering suggests cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) as another possible sub-category. Finally, the paper discusses practical implementation and optimization, which relates to cs.SE (Software Engineering).
